_sText:
This is simply de_dust with the new additions seen in 
video previews for the upcoming Counter-Strike :
Global Offensive videos. CS:GO is the "new" Counter-
Strike scheduled to come out next year. The is NOT a 
complete reimagining of the map, or an exact copy of 
the awesomeness that is going to be the new de_dust! I 
simply tried to implimented a few of the core map 
changes into the existing original de_dust.  


>T Spawn closer to the underpass.
>Added stairs from the underpass to the top.
>Moved bomsite B closer to the middle.
>Added a brigde.
>Also added a couple boxes here and there.
